title: #92Noon! Leber/Barreiro/Lucia!
description: First hour of talkers, Leber in studio, Wolves VP Brad Ruiter joins on Wolves event for remembering Flip Saunders, Barreiro calls in to share Flip stories, and Gopher Hockey coach Don Lucia closes the show!
